item.title: The Hollywood Reporter’s Power Broker Awards Toast Winners and Unity in the Wake of L.A. Fires
item.description: The fifth annual event, presented by The Society Group, recognized the biggest names in Los Angeles real estate after a tumultuous year for the city.
